get you through the weekend.

245
00:17:40,333 --> 00:17:42,708
[SENJI]
Hey... Champ.

246
00:17:47,666 --> 00:17:49,750
Look... I, uh...

247
00:17:49,833 --> 00:17:54,250
Hell of a fight.
Much respect, Ganta.

248
00:17:59,250 --> 00:18:00,791
[GANTA] Yeah!

249
00:18:03,041 --> 00:18:05,375
[FEMALE ANCHOR 5-A] Thanks
for watching news at eight.

250
00:18:05,458 --> 00:18:07,708
I was so afraid
of him... but...

251
00:18:07,791 --> 00:18:09,125
[GAME SHOW MUSIC]

252
00:18:09,208 --> 00:18:13,083
Maybe... me and Senji
are gonna be okay now...

253
00:18:15,708 --> 00:18:17,791
Hey! What's
clucking, everyone?

254
00:18:17,875 --> 00:18:22,166
It's time for the Carnival
Corpse post-game treat!

255
00:18:22,250 --> 00:18:25,833
It's... the "Too Bad
for the Loser Show!"

256
00:18:27,625 --> 00:18:29,458
Huh...?

257
00:18:29,541 --> 00:18:31,208
Wait, that's...

258
00:18:39,791 --> 00:18:41,000
Hi there, Senji.

259
00:18:41,083 --> 00:18:43,750
I hope your luck has
improved since the fight.

260
00:18:48,416 --> 00:18:51,625
Hold up...
What's going on?

261
00:18:58,250 --> 00:18:59,916
[SENJI] Just do it.

262
00:19:03,041 --> 00:19:04,500
[TAKASHIMA]
The right eye.

263
00:19:04,583 --> 00:19:05,666
Huh...?

264
00:19:30,125 --> 00:19:31,416
[GANTA GASPS]

265
00:19:32,333 --> 00:19:37,333
[SENJI YELLS IN AGONY]

266
00:19:50,791 --> 00:19:53,791
[SENJI BREATHES HEAVILY]

267
00:19:56,166 --> 00:19:56,791
[GANTA RETCHES]

268
00:19:56,875 --> 00:19:58,791
[EXPLOSION]

269
00:20:00,166 --> 00:20:02,250
What... the hell?!

270
00:20:03,083 --> 00:20:04,791
[SHIRO YELLS ANGRILY]

271
00:20:04,875 --> 00:20:09,250
[FIGHTING SOUNDS]

272
00:20:09,333 --> 00:20:10,791
[GLASS SHATTERS]

273
00:20:10,875 --> 00:20:11,625
--What's happening up there?!
--[SHIRO] Don't take me away

274
00:20:11,708 --> 00:20:13,583
from Ganta, you meanies!

275
00:20:13,666 --> 00:20:14,583
[GUARD 5-A CHOKES]

276
00:20:14,666 --> 00:20:15,458
[ALARM SOUNDS]

277
00:20:15,541 --> 00:20:16,500
This is control...!

278
00:20:16,583 --> 00:20:17,791
What's going on here?!

279
00:20:17,875 --> 00:20:20,250
SR-4...!
Come in, dammit!

280
00:20:20,333 --> 00:20:21,541
[YOH]
Armed uprising, sir!

281
00:20:21,625 --> 00:20:23,375
We're gonna need back-up ASAP!

282
00:20:23,458 --> 00:20:25,708
If they force their
way into the system...!

283
00:20:25,791 --> 00:20:27,375
You gotta shut down
the electricity

284
00:20:27,458 --> 00:20:29,500
in this cell-block... please!

285
00:20:29,583 --> 00:20:30,500
[CONTROL TOWER
COMMANDER] Understood!

286
00:20:30,583 --> 00:20:32,166
Armored guards are
on their way.

287
00:20:32,250 --> 00:20:33,583
But who's running the show?

288
00:20:33,666 --> 00:20:36,458
How many perps
are we talking here?!

289
00:20:36,541 --> 00:20:38,208
There's only one, sir...

290
00:20:38,291 --> 00:20:41,250
Just a single, solitary
girl with snow-white hair.

291
00:20:41,333 --> 00:20:46,291
[Instrumental "Lullaby"]

292
00:21:05,750 --> 00:21:07,541
Damn it, that little
girl is insane!

293
00:21:07,625 --> 00:21:10,166
I don't like how it got
quiet all of a sudden.

294
00:21:10,250 --> 00:21:12,791
Where the hell is she?

295
00:21:12,875 --> 00:21:17,583
The lullaby... it stopped.

296
00:21:20,750 --> 00:21:21,916
[GUNS COCK]

297
00:21:22,000 --> 00:21:23,125
[GUARD DETAIL LEADER]
Perpetrator confirmed!

298
00:21:23,208 --> 00:21:25,833
Extreme prejudice, gentlemen!

299
00:21:30,750 --> 00:21:32,708
[DOOR SQUEAKS OPEN]

300
00:21:32,791 --> 00:21:34,416
I really owe you one, Shiro!

301
00:21:34,500 --> 00:21:38,166
Thanks a lot for being a decoy
and distracting 'em all for me.

302
00:21:38,250 --> 00:21:41,166
[EXPLOSION]

303
00:21:49,375 --> 00:21:51,416
[THUD]

304
00:21:51,500 --> 00:21:54,375
[GANTA RETCHES]

305
00:21:54,458 --> 00:21:57,416
[GANTA COUGHS]

306
00:22:01,291 --> 00:22:02,125
[THUD]

307
00:22:02,208 --> 00:22:06,291
[GANTA THINKING]
You forgot...

308
00:22:06,375 --> 00:22:08,458
Stupid...

309
00:22:24,375 --> 00:22:26,250
[GANTA THINKING]
It's a madhouse...

310
00:22:26,333 --> 00:22:29,208
...and you're locked inside it.

311
00:22:31,125 --> 00:22:33,083
[YOH GASPS]

312
00:22:36,125 --> 00:22:40,291
[GANTA THINKING]
You can't forget... Not ever...

313
00:22:44,750 --> 00:22:46,583
This is real...

314
00:22:46,666 --> 00:22:50,708
This is your whole world now...

315
00:22:50,791 --> 00:22:53,083
Deadman Wonderland...

316
00:22:53,166 --> 00:22:55,208
That's what they call it...

317
00:22:55,291 --> 00:22:58,541
But really... it's hell.

318
00:23:08,166 --> 00:23:13,125
♪ closing song ♪

319
00:24:39,000 --> 00:24:41,833
[MAKINA] When the lullaby
ends and the egg laughs...

320
00:24:41,916 --> 00:24:44,666
...the world will
drown in absurdity.

321
00:24:44,750 --> 00:24:47,666
Branch of Sin is
different for everybody...

322
00:24:47,750 --> 00:24:50,750
You can look at the flower
all you want, Woodpecker...

323
00:24:50,833 --> 00:24:53,041
...but mind those thorns.

